body: Looking for a new dynasty startup with great people,  any tips?

10 Great Tips for Pitching Your Startup.
1. Be passionate.
2. Make it snappy.
3. Don't state the obvious.
4. Mention the big stuff first.  
5. Use analogies. 
7. Ditch the formula. 
8. Give them a reason. 
9. Be fair. 
10. Sell a vision.
